General.Name: Panther Metals Ltd
General.Description: Panther Metals Ltd engages in the exploration of mineral properties in Australia. The company primarily explores for nickel, cobalt, and gold deposits. It holds 100% interest in Coglia, Red Flag, Merolia, and Mikado projects located in Laverton, Western Australia; and Marraki and Annaburroo projects situated in Northern Territory. Panther Metals Ltd was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Perth, Australia.
